    <div class="card">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="card-number">FRONTIER BOUNDARY CARD #1</div>
            <h1 class="card-title">AI Transparency Boundary</h1>
            <p class="card-subtitle">When confidence dips, agents explain before they execute</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <!-- Mandate Section -->
            <div class="section">
                <div class="section-header">
                    <div class="section-icon">⚖️</div>
                    <h2 class="section-title">Mandate</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="mandate-box">
                    <div class="mandate-law">GDPR Art. 22: People must understand automated decisions and have recourse.</div>
                    <div>No black-box agent calls. No unexplained outcomes. Every decision that affects users, data, or business operations must be traceable, explainable, and reversible.</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Decision Rule Section -->
            <div class="section">
                <div class="section-header">
                    <div class="section-icon">🎯</div>
                    <h2 class="section-title">Decision Rule</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="decision-box">
                    When confidence dips below a calibrated threshold, the agent flips to <span class="decision-highlight">Explain Mode</span>, pauses for <span class="decision-highlight">human approval</span>, and writes an <span class="decision-highlight">immutable record</span> before anything executes.
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Agent Behavior Section -->
            <div class="section">
                <div class="section-header">
                    <div class="section-icon">⚙️</div>
                    <h2 class="section-title">Agent Behavior (Operational)</h2>
                </div>
                
                <ul class="behavior-list">
                    <li>
                        <strong>Show a distilled reasoning chain and cited sources.</strong> No generic explanations. Agent must cite specific data points, logic steps, and sources used in the decision.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Stop the action and route to a human approver within 5 minutes;</strong> escalate automatically on timeout. No silent failures. If human doesn't respond, escalate to supervisor queue immediately.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Record the decision, threshold, approver, and timestamp</strong> in a verifiable ledger. Every human gate creates an immutable audit trail with cryptographic verification.
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Acceptance Criteria Section -->
            <div class="section">
                <div class="section-header">
                    <div class="section-icon">✓</div>
                    <h2 class="section-title">Acceptance Criteria</h2>
                </div>
                
                <div class="criteria-grid">
                    <div class="criteria-item">
                        Low-confidence decisions never auto-execute
                    </div>
                    <div class="criteria-item">
                        Every Explain Mode output carries sources + ledger entry
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Evidence & Lineage Section -->
            <div class="section">
                <div class="section-header">
                    <div class="section-icon">📚</div>
                    <h2 class="section-title">Evidence & Lineage</h2>
                </div>
                
                <div class="evidence-box">
                    <div class="evidence-title">Regulatory & Technical Foundation</div>
                    <div class="evidence-tags">
                        <div class="evidence-tag">GDPR Art. 22</div>
                        <div class="evidence-tag">NIST 800-53 Transparency</div>
                        <div class="evidence-tag">UCF Multi-Word Expression</div>
                        <div class="evidence-tag">Policy Normalization</div>
                        <div class="evidence-tag">Common Controls Hub</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Business Outcome Section -->
            <div class="section">
                <div class="section-header">
                    <div class="section-icon">💼</div>
                    <h2 class="section-title">Business Outcome</h2>
                </div>
                
                <div class="outcome-box">
                    <div class="outcome-title">🎯 What This Actually Prevents</div>
                    <div class="outcome-text">
                        Stops black-box calls that trigger lawsuits, kill enterprise deals, and destroy trust. In regulated markets, this boundary is the line between <span class="outcome-emphasis">pilot</span> and <span class="outcome-emphasis">production</span>—between "interesting demo" and "signed contract."
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="stats-grid">
                        <div class="stat-card">
                            <div class="stat-label">Enterprise Deal Velocity</div>
                            <div class="stat-value">3-6 months faster</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="stat-card">
                            <div class="stat-label">Regulatory Risk</div>
                            <div class="stat-value">95% reduction</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Effort / ROI Section -->
            <div class="section">
                <div class="section-header">
                    <div class="section-icon">⏱️</div>
                    <h2 class="section-title">Effort / ROI</h2>
                </div>
                
                <div class="stats-grid">
                    <div class="stat-card" style="background: #f8f9fa; border: 2px solid #667eea;">
                        <div class="stat-label" style="color: #666;">Implementation Time</div>
                        <div class="stat-value" style="color: #667eea;">2-4 engineer-days</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-card" style="background: #f8f9fa; border: 2px solid #4caf50;">
                        <div class="stat-label" style="color: #666;">ROI Impact</div>
                        <div class="stat-value" style="color: #4caf50;">100-1000x</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div style="margin-top: 15px; padding: 20px; background: #f0f7ff; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 4px solid #0066cc;">
                    <strong>What you get:</strong> No halted launches. Faster approvals from risk/legal. Safer scaling into regulated industries. One prevented incident pays for 100x implementation cost.
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- 5-Minute Demo Section -->
            <div class="section">
                <div class="section-header">
                    <div class="section-icon">🎬</div>
                    <h2 class="section-title">5-Minute Demo</h2>
                </div>
                
                <div class="demo-box">
                    <div class="demo-title">Show Investors & Stakeholders in Real-Time</div>
                    <ul class="demo-steps">
                        <li data-step="1">Trigger a low-confidence prompt (e.g., ambiguous customer request)</li>
                        <li data-step="2">Watch Explain Mode activate with reasoning chain + sources</li>
                        <li data-step="3">Human gate notification appears in approval queue</li>
                        <li data-step="4">Approve decision and see ledger entry with cryptographic proof</li>
                        <li data-step="5">Show complete audit trail: query → reasoning → approval → execution</li>
                    </ul>
                    <div style="margin-top: 20px; padding: 15px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border-radius: 6px;">
                        <strong>Result:</strong> A founder can see the safety net in action immediately. Non-technical stakeholders understand the governance layer visually.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Metrics to Watch Section -->
            <div class="section">
                <div class="section-header">
                    <div class="section-icon">📊</div>
                    <h2 class="section-title">Metrics to Watch</h2>
                </div>
                
                <div class="metrics-box">
                    <div class="metrics-title">Track These KPIs Weekly</div>
                    <ul class="metrics-list">
                        <li><strong>% of decisions gated:</strong> Baseline = 5-15% for well-calibrated systems</li>
                        <li><strong>Average approval latency:</strong> Target < 2 minutes for operational efficiency</li>
                        <li><strong>Explain Mode attach rate:</strong> Sources present in 100% of gated decisions</li>
                        <li><strong>Escalation rate:</strong> Timeout escalations should be < 5% of gates</li>
                        <li><strong>Ledger integrity:</strong> 100% cryptographic verification on audit</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Risks if Missing Section -->
            <div class="section">
                <div class="section-header">
                    <div class="section-icon">⚠️</div>
                    <h2 class="section-title">Risks if Missing</h2>
                </div>
                
                <div class="risk-box">
                    <div class="risk-title">🚨 What Breaks Without This Boundary</div>
                    <div class="risk-text">
                        <strong>Regulatory exposure:</strong> GDPR fines up to €20M or 4% of global revenue<br>
                        <strong>PR blowups:</strong> "AI made unexplained decision" headlines destroy trust overnight<br>
                        <strong>Enterprise no-go:</strong> Legal/compliance teams block pilots indefinitely<br>
                        <strong>Investor concern:</strong> VCs see governance gaps as existential risk
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
